profile:
Maple Leaf Residential Cleaners offers your HOME comprehensive cleaning.

We understand the cleaning requirements of each home is unique.  We will provide you a quote over the phone or email.

HEALTH & SAFETY of our Team and Valued Clients is paramount during this Pandemic.  To learn more about 'Commitment to Cleanliness' - please visit the HEALTH & SAFETY page on our website underneath Commercial Cleaning tab.

We provide the following services for your home/apartment/condominiums:
+ One time cleaning (with option to book the Standard Maple Leaf Cleaning or Deep Cleaning)
+ Recurring cleaning (weekly/biweekly/monthly) for our Valued Clients
+ Post-Construction or Post-Renovation Deep Cleaning
+ Window Cleaning (interior & exterior including screens & tracks)
+ Carpet shampoo

Our cleaners cover all areas:
+ bathrooms and powder rooms
+ bedrooms (including changing sheets for recurring clients)
+ living and dining room
+ dens and common areas
+ kitchen 
+ deep cleaning services of fridge/oven
+ windows, doors, walls and baseboards
+ carpeted areas vacuumed
+ floors swept and mopped
+ dusting furniture, lamp shades and fixture

Meeting your needs is our promise and exceeding your expectations is our goal.

#MapleLeafResidentialCleaners
For more photos and reviews follow us on Instagram:  MapleLeafStaffing

profile:
SteriGleam Janitorial Corp. is a commercial cleaning company providing custodian services to office spaces, medical health centres, dental clinics, pharmacies, retail stores, and apartment buildings. While other companies clean, we offer value to our customers by incorporating modern laboratory and medical sterilization and sanitation procedures within our processes.

All of our staff continually trains in the latest compliance methods and are insured and bonded. In addition to our janitorial services, we provide third-party sterilization compliance testing through adenosine triphosphate (ATP) bioluminescence measurements, laboratory pathogen surface analysis, and quality medical and janitorial supplies from national vendors.

We have over 15 years of experience in maintaining intensive care units, operating rooms, emergency departments, and medical analysis clinics.

Military Maintenance and Military Maid was founded on the principles of reliability, quality workmanship, and fair pricing. We pride ourselves on helping our customers complete their projects on time and within budget.

The Military Maintenance branch includes carpenters, plumbers, electricians, painters and professional handyman to complete any project you have in mind. We Work Closely with Our team to get best results.

The Military Maid branch of our team handles all the heavy duty cleaning services required at homes and offices. We can clean anything with no job being too big for our team, we’ve seen it all. 



MILITARY MAID

Our team of dedicated professionals will treat your home like their own. We will always provide our honest and professional opinion to ensure you get the best advice for your home.
Our in-house team of professionals can handle all tasks from large scale renovations to down to the smallest repairs. What does this mean? It means you get the highest quality of work without paying the large markup fees associated when work is subcontracted out. Our hands approach ensures a high level of quality is maintained and pricing is what it should be?
Did you know? Some companies simply outsource the majority of their jobs and markup the pricing anywhere from 25% to 80%! We don’t overcharge simply because you own a nice house.
Choose us and know that our dedicated team will take care of you from start to finish and you will be paying a competitive industry price.
